data.description: This lakefront view 2 bedroom 2 bath unit is ready for a new owner. Kings Point - Trent community is a active gated adult community and has all the amenities such as pool, community room, fitness center, hobby room, library, tennis courts, billiard room, theater, etc...Community's bus for your convenience to shopping centers, malls, etc.. Social clubs and interest groups of all types.  Primary bedroom spacious with walk in closet. Washer and dryer in unit. No renting allowed.
